Bafana Bafana attacker Percy Tau has won the Proximus League Player of the Season award following his scintillating first season with Belgian second division side Union Saint-Gilloise. The 24-year-old star player moved to Belgium at the begining of the season. But he quickly found his foot in the league and continue with his outstanding display which saw him being crowne Absa Premiership Player of the season last campaign when he was still playing for Mamelodi Sundowns.  